data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Welcome to your dream home in Port Richey, Florida! Nestled on a spacious lot and a half, this charming residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and Florida living. With 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, and 1,450 square feet of well-designed living space, this home is a haven for relaxation and enjoyment. As you approach, you'll be greeted by the captivating curb appeal and the durability of an 8-year-old metal roof, ensuring both aesthetic appeal and long-lasting protection. The home is strategically situated on a hill, providing picturesque views and a sense of tranquility that's unique to this property. Step inside, and you'll discover a thoughtfully designed interior with an abundance of natural light, creating an inviting and warm atmosphere. The spacious living areas seamlessly connect, offering an ideal layout for both entertaining and everyday living. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring modern appliances, ample counter space, and a convenient layout that makes meal preparation a breeze. The three well-appointed bedrooms provide comfortable retreats, with the master bedroom boasting an en-suite bathroom for added privacy and convenience. The two additional bedrooms share a tastefully appointed bathroom, ensuring comfort for family and guests alike. One of the highlights of this home is the backyard oasis. Step outside to discover a delightful partially submerged above-ground pool, perfect for cooling off on hot Florida days or enjoying a refreshing swim under the sunny skies. The pool area is complemented by a spacious patio, creating an ideal setting for outdoor gatherings, barbecues, or simply lounging by the pool.  Port Richey's year-round pleasant weather allows you to make the most of outdoor living, and this home provides the perfect space to do just that. Whether you're relaxing by the pool, enjoying the scenic views from the hillside, or hosting gatherings with friends and family, this property is a true gem. Use the other portion of the backyard for gardening or outdoor games! Conveniently located in Port Richey, you'll have easy access to local amenities, schools, parks, and the beautiful Gulf Coast beaches. Don't miss the opportunity to make this 3-bedroom, 2-bath, 1,450 sqft pool home with an 8-year-old metal roof your own piece of Florida paradise. Welcome home!
